      GetAllLinkRefs←{
    ⍝ This combs through the html and finds all link references ([][]-syntax).
    ⍝ Ignores in-line code.
    ⍝ Returns a three-item-vector for each hit.
    ⍝ [1] The link text - that can by anything.
